data.eml:eml: A new species of Fansipaniana from Northern Vietnam (Lepidoptera: Tortricidae: Olethreutinae: Olethreutini)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Heppner, John B., Bae, Yang-Seop (2016): A new species of Fansipaniana from Northern Vietnam (Lepidoptera: Tortricidae: Olethreutinae: Olethreutini). Zootaxa 4097 (1): 135-138, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4097.1.10
